data.description: Welcome to your charming retreat in Arcadia, Florida! This meticulously upgraded 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom modular home spans 1275 sq ft and is nestled on a sprawling 1-acre lot. Boasting modern comforts, this residence has undergone significant enhancements, making it a haven of convenience and style. Owners just installed new well pump and entire acre boasts irrigation system.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a brand-new kitchen featuring top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances and contemporary finishes. The heart of the home, this kitchen is a chef's delight, perfect for creating culinary masterpieces. The premium vinyl flooring seamlessly flows throughout the entire home, providing both durability and a touch of elegance.  The living spaces are bathed in natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. With a new A/C unit, your comfort is assured, while the upcoming new roof installation in February 2024 adds an extra layer of security and longevity to your investment. The upgraded electrical panel ensures modern efficiency and safety.    Escape to the screened lanai, where you can enjoy the Florida sunshine and gentle breezes in a serene outdoor setting. The expansive 1-acre lot provides ample space for outdoor activities, gardening, or even the possibility of adding personalized touches to make it your own oasis.  Conveniently located just 15 minutes away from I-75 and Punta Gorda FL, this residence offers easy access to major transportation routes, making your daily commute or weekend getaways a breeze. Whether you're looking for a peaceful retreat or a home that effortlessly blends modern amenities with the tranquility of nature, this Arcadia gem is the perfect place to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautifully updated modular home yours!
